644c19adf2d9b4568853", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/apache/hadoop/git/trees/3fcf49ba7fec0b3ccfe9644c19adf2d9b4568853"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/apache/hadoop/git/commits/2005582a28b47ce7aac35702c485559fd62e6a90", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": true, "reason": "valid", "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsBcBAABCAAQBQJi9WwXCRBK7hj4Ov3rIwAA3BkIAEg1TN0J+hwQSuUMhBce15fX\nKiVm1i2uyANuXggtBR/CkZ8j8d+HVwVfNWlJl6HTZI1YhYn6t+qAUL+urxFepTT4\n71JEDiqF0ND1caoRzlIdcfVqgFa5knP3Z9CpFHi+fUK7+bTOHeOSTeI7Aufoy1vK\nD989RIEhWQGDmNtVH2zpX1+BJJxcVxW/nk7arvCjJhxaoJpUlBXknp49uoEPUyVt\nxRZ59vWQJRn0Unp7nU4aVatpneE9L/2/lIesuZholbGBTr1nOsYqynLQ6vHj8K3A\nEZr3WUiErHln+fv6n6UjE2iiAB5IRVKj5ihIfvzPIaNx2ILxyGMARH+J1Mo/2aY=\n=0Fog\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n", "payload": "tree 3fcf49ba7fec0b3ccfe9644c19adf2d9b4568853\nparent 6ca2d3f8482491fc4e2a81324f47af77a1bddfaa\nauthor Steve Vaughan <email@stevevaughan.me> 1660251159 -0400\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1660251159 -0700\n\nHDFS-16702. MiniDFSCluster should report cause of exception in assert error (#4680)\n\nWhen the MiniDFSClsuter detects that an exception caused an exit, it should include that exception as the cause for the AssertionError that it throws. The current AssertError simply reports the message \"Test resulted in an unexpected exit\" and provides a stack trace to the location of the check for an exit exception. This patch adds the original exception as the cause of the AssertError.\r\n", "verified_at": "2024-01-16T19:59:59Z"}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/apache/hadoop/commits/2005582a28b47ce7aac35702c485559fd62e6a90", "html_url": "https://github.com/apache/hadoop/commit/2005582a28b47ce7aac35702c485559fd62e6a90", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/apache/hadoop/commits/2005582a28b47ce7aac35702c485559fd62e6a90/comments", "author": {"login": "snmvaughan", "id": 374920, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjM3NDkyMA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/